h1. DB

h2. Purpose

Returns the MongoDB [DB|http://api.mongodb.org/java/current/com/mongodb/DB.html] object.

h2. Examples

{code:java}
def dbCollection = Book.DB.getCollection("books")
{code}

h2. Description

The @DB@ property allows access to the underlying MongoDB [DB|http://api.mongodb.org/java/current/com/mongodb/DB.html] object, thus allowing easy access to the low-level MongoDB Java driver.
